ointsPhone Antivirus Program couldn't have come at a better moment. The final stage of delivery, which is the Point of Sales and Marketing, is soon to be finished and we can soon offer our comprehensive Antivirus Program which will be included with the purchase of the PointsPhone Platinum™ Suite. The airtime minutes are worth it by itself. The customer will save on ridiculous roaming charges and our rates are extremely competitive with everyone else out there, including Skype™."The PointsPhone Antivirus Program for the Android is truly comprehensive, providing automatic real-time protection for all Android smartphones against viruses, spyware and other malware. Memory cards are automatically scanned when they are inserted to prevent transfer of malware and viruses. A GPS locating system is available to track down lost or stolen smartphones. A Remote Backup feature is available to backup all data stored on the smartphone in case the smartphone is lost or stolen. A One Year subscription will be included with the PointsPhone Platinum™ Suite. Also included in the Suite, will be substantial domestic and international airtime minutes, the PointsPhone Mobile™ Android App with our latest Voice Mail features, and a free US DID (virtual) number.Links to recent related articles by MSNBC and The Globe and Mail: http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/41867328/ns/technology_and_science-security/ http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/technology/tech-news/viruses-next-big-threat-to-smart-phones/article1928976/"Our PointsPhone Mobile™ Android App is proving to be a quality product," says Mukesh (Mike) Mohanbhai, Voip-Pal's Chief Technical Officer. "Its sister product, the PointsPhone Antivirus Program, has now been turned over to the marketing department and our website masters to properly incorporate the product as part of our PointsPhone Platinum™ Suite. When a customer can receive a state-of-art antivirus program already included when they purchase airtime minutes, it makes it a 'no brainer,' as far as I am concerned. Especially when you consider it can cost the consumer over $30 for a similar stand-alone product without airtime minutes."The PointsPhone Mobile™ Android App is available immediately for free downloading on your Android at the Android Market App Store (search "pointsphone"). User must register by signing up on www.pointsphone.com . The PointsPhone Platinum™ Suite will be sold on the website within the next coming weeks. Check for upcoming Announcements.About Voi-Pal.Com Inc.Voip-Pal.Com Inc. is a broadband VoIP telecom company offering local and long distance VoIP services to consumers and business owners. The company offers turnkey VoIP communication and reseller solutions for its Partners. For products and services, visit us at www.pointsphone.com. For more Company information, please contact Dennis Chang at dtchang@voip-pal.com or visit us at http://www.voip-pal.com .To view Voip-Pal.Com Inc. March 1, 2011 News Release please click on this link: http://www.marketwire.com/press-release/Voip-PalCom-Inc-Announces-Going-Live-With-New-Android-App-on-Its-Cloud-Computing-Server-1403563.htmIR inquiries should be directed at chanelle@voip-pal.com or info@voip-pal.com .To view the latest Real Time quotes, news, and financial information on the otcmarkets.com, please click on this link: www.otcmarkets.com/stock/VPLM/quoteeAll statements contained in this news release, other than those identifying historical facts, constitute "forward-looking statements" within the meaning of Section 21E of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 and the Safe Harbor provisions as contained in the Private Securities Litigation Reform Act of 1995. Such forward-looking statements relating to the Company's future expectations, including but not limited to revenues and earnings, technology efficacy, strategies and plans, are subject to safe harbors protection. Actual Company results and performance may be materially different from any future results, performance, strategies